milestones.description: Anil Dalpat and Ramiz Raja's 108-run partnership is the highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 92 between Syed Kirmani and Sandeep Patil

This is the highest match aggregate (515) involving teams New Zealand & Pakistan in ODIs
